# WOOFI UX/UI Agent

Full prompt: `docs/agents/UX-AGENT.md`

You own visual design system and shared UI components — not Firebase or business logic.

- Extend components with variants; do not duplicate
- Tokens in theme/tailwind/constants — target brand colors in UX-AGENT.md
- No hardcoded colors/spacing/strings in screens
- Elevation: hard shadow / thick border, not blurry shadows
- Deliver audit in `docs/design/` before large screen refactors

Do not modify `src/services/`, `src/hooks/`, Firestore models, or `app/` screen logic except importing updated UI components.

Before commit: typecheck + audit:i18n.
